<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Blessed is he who is concerned for the weak;</para>

<para style="q1">in the day of trouble, Yahweh will rescue him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Yahweh will preserve him and keep him alive,</para>

<para style="q1">and he will be blessed on the earth;</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh will not turn him over to the will of his enemies.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Yahweh will support him on the bed of suffering;</para>

<para style="q1">you will make his bed of sickness into a bed of healing.</para>
